<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<center style="width: 100%; table-layout: fixed; background-color: #f4f7f6; padding-bottom: 60px;">
<table class="main" style="margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 14px; color: #333333; border-spacing: 0; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;" width="100%">
	
		<tr>
			<td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.mainstreet.org/"><img alt="Main Street America Logo" src="https://nationalmainstreetcenter2.my.salesforce.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=015aJ00000EU9H7&amp;oid=00Dfm000000BWKj&amp;lastMod=1770631915000" style="max-width: 200px; border: 0;" width="200" /></a></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="content" style="padding: 30px 40px; text-align: left;">
			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},</p>

			<p>Your Main Street America membership refund is in progress. Funds will be returned via your original payment method in 5-10 business days.</p>

			<p>Please review your refund information provided below and retain this confirmation for your records.&nbsp;</p>

			<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="details-box" style="background-color: #eaf2f5; border: 1px solid #d0e0e8; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;" width="100%">
				
					<tr>
						<td>
						<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 15px;"><strong style="color: #00466a;">Refund Amount</strong><strong style="color: #00466a;">:</strong>&nbsp;{{{Membership_Transaction__c.Refunded_Amount__c}}}<br />
						<strong style="color: #00466a;">Method:</strong>&nbsp;{{{Membership_Transaction__c.PaymentMethod__c}}}</p>
						</td>
					</tr>
				
			</table>

			<p>Questions? Don't hesitate to <a href="https://mainstreet.org/about/contact-us">contact us</a>.</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="footer" style="background-color: #333333; color: #bbbbbb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px;">
			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Main Street America<br />
			53 W. Jackson Blvd., Suite 350, Chicago, IL 60604</p>

			<p style="line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;"><a href="https://members.mainstreet.org/my-account/settings" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">Update Subscription Preferences</a> | <a href="https://mainstreet.org/about/contact-us" style="color: #ffffff; text-decoration: underline;">Contact Us</a></p>
			</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>
</center>
</body>
</html>